{"tid":2202054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑藏氣槍雷射筆 無業男稱遭女警恐嚇招認 官拒絕接納招認證供呈堂","createTime":"2020-09-14T09:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T09:47:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de73aeeb92be90e5025e792e44b05ae347751dcf","tid":2202054,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"警方去年12月在沙田好運中心截查無業男時，聲稱在其背包內搜出內有鋼珠的氣槍及雷射筆。無業男被控管有攻擊性武器及管有仿製火器罪，案件今於沙田法院開審。控方指被告警誡下承認以雷射筆照射警員及警署，又將氣槍內的鋼珠數目及直徑告知警員。惟辯方反對將被告的招認口供呈堂，指曾有女警恐嚇「堅持話冇就坐10年啦」，所謂招認實情是警員將自己調查的內容綜合得出，然後要求被告簽署口供。裁判官溫紹明最後裁定控方不能將被告的招認口供呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n女警疑稱：你一定係收咗錢出嚟出來做嘢<br />\n其後補錄口供時，有女警突然進入房內，向被告稱「你一定係收咗錢出嚟出來做嘢」，被告當場否認：女警再指「堅持話無就坐10年啦」。最終在何不斷的催促下，被告沒有看口供內容便簽署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/5M463R5ZTFCWHJJKVC3HCMK25E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2F5M463R5ZTFCWHJJKVC3HCMK25E%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=5b08f6ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2F5M463R5ZTFCWHJJKVC3HCMK25E%2F&h=3cd24089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/5M463R5ZTFCWHJJKVC3HCMK25E/</a>"},{"pid":"16c4cc3ddde1496fd8f4d32edd54e7d79ee047cd","tid":2202054,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761ba14f1efcdb5888be9a67fd33369817bd0b4a","tid":2202054,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c7984ff046e413279b531c2efea3f671320b79","tid":2202054,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"名真係唔好亂簽, 一時之快有排煩<br />\n除時判你證供有效, 睇個官點睇"},{"pid":"551ba92898362b4231596ef810eeeb82e6995a6f","tid":2202054,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"兩腳狗：無後果點解唔老屈啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ff337def9533a7400b4124b0efc5212364266f","tid":2202054,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:47:36.000Z","msg":"辯方表示被告的招認極不尋常，警員指被告曾稱「在<span class=\"red\">示威行動</span>中使用雷射筆」，惟辯方認為「示威活動」是警方常用字眼，被告沒有說過相關字眼<br />\n<br />\n毅進仔真係毅進仔<br />\n作口供都作得柒過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}